0xD29D8EDD.name: GET_MAPDATA_FROM_HASH_KEY
0xD29D8EDD.description:
Returns the transient map data index for a specified hash.
This function supports SDK infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
0xD29D8EDD.resultsDescription: A transient (non-persistable) index to the requested mapdata, or -1.
